'Tanda tangan ini berbeda.'

00:20:36.920 --> 00:20:39.655 line:20%
'Huruf 'R' terlihat
cukup bulat di sini'

00:20:39.680 --> 00:20:41.040 line:20%
'dan huruf 'S' juga
terlihat sangat berbeda.'

00:20:41.240 --> 00:20:42.840 line:20%
'Orang lain telah menandatanganinya.'

00:20:43.040 --> 00:20:44.440 line:20%
'Keluarkan kausmu dan balikkan.'

00:20:48.800 --> 00:20:50.240 line:20%
'Preesha, apa yang kamu lihat?'

00:20:50.400 --> 00:20:51.520 line:20%
'Hatiku benar.'

00:20:51.840 --> 00:20:52.960 line:20%
'Kamu pasti Rudra-ku.'

00:20:53.152 --> 00:20:54.272 line:20%
'Ya, aku Rudramu.'

00:20:54.560 --> 00:20:55.800 line:20%
'Apakah ada Rudra lain
yang menggantikanku?'

00:20:55.915 --> 00:20:57.040 line:20%
'Ya ada satu'

